metadata.description:
Landspeeder.
Mondo comes to the Mos Espa market to buy a Speeder. But the seller is asking too much.What came of it?

MP4
3860 x 2170

Mini Mondo. Animated series about Mandalorian and Grogu. Small funny stories about what could be left behind the scenes. That's the way.
